'''Tomas Alfredson''' (born 1 April 1965) is a [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[film director]] and a member of the Swedish comedy group [[Killingg<U+00E4>nget]] as a director since [[1999]]. 

Alfredson is the son of [[Hans Alfredson]] and the brother of [[Daniel Alfredson (director)|Daniel Alfredson]]. 

